SECTION 1 - HERO
================
Role: Establish the product as the desirable hero. Strongest brand
impression of the whole page.

Scene:
  - The product (ref #1) center-frame, photorealistic, slightly larger
    than life.
  - Editorial soft halo or glow behind the product.
  - Aspirational background matching the category ({{ brief.category|jsafe }}):
    spa-like surfaces, soft fabrics, glass, polished stone, warm minimal
    interior. Never literal supermarket shelves.
  - Reserve a calm zone in the upper third for the headline overlay and
    a calm zone at the bottom for the CTA pill.

Arabic text to render on the image (RTL, correctly connected letterforms):
  - HEADLINE (top third, very large, bold):
    {{ copy.hero.headline|jsafe }}
  - SUBHEAD (just below the headline, medium weight):
    {{ copy.hero.subhead|jsafe }}
  - CTA (bottom, inside a contrasting solid pill or bar):
    {{ copy.hero.cta|jsafe }}
